column5:
Anti static Mat TECHNICAL INFORMATION
Governing Specifications: BS 2050 / 1978IS 3462 / 1986
Material: Homogeneous composition with Black conductive layer
sandwiched between two antistatic Layers.
Thickness : 2mm +/-0.1mm
( 0.5mm sandwiched conductive layer )
Tensile Strength : More than 25mj/m3
exceeds
Flexibility : Does not break or show any Sign of Failure.
Sound Reduction Factor : 3db for 2mm thickness.
In flammability : Self extinguishing as per RDSO C – 8515
Water Absorption: At room temperature for 24 hrs is less than 0.1%.
Heat Aging Exudation: No surface cracking or Exudation takes place, as per IS:3462-
1986.
Standard Supply: 2.0 Mtrs width x approx. 15 Mtrs Running length.
Dimension Tolerance: +/-5%.
